longBusinessSummary: First America Resources Corporation does not have significant operations. Previously, it was involved in selling lithium-ion batteries and related power supplies that are primarily used in mobile and consumer electronics products. The company was formerly known as Golden Oasis New Energy Group, Inc. and changed its name to First America Resources Corporation in August 2014. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Morris, Illinois.
